    <h1>NAP Consistency</h1>
    <p class="description">The practice of keeping your business <strong>Name, Address, and Phone number</strong> identical across every directory, website, and social profile — a foundational local SEO signal that determines whether Google trusts your listing enough to show it.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
